SRM code dependencies
=====================

SRM version 1.1 support.


* Globus libraries (for GSI)
  Makefile uses $GLOBUS_LOCATION

* CGSI plugin (dev)
  > wget http://castor.web.cern.ch/castor/DIST/CERN/savannah/CGSI_gSOAP.pkg/2.6-1.1.9/CGSI_gSOAP_2.6-dev-1.1.9-1.slc3.i386.rpm
  > rpm -Uvh CGSI_gSOAP_2.6-dev-1.1.9-1.slc3.i386.rpm

  Makefile uses default location:
  /usr/include/cgsi_plugin.h
  /usr/lib/libcgsi_plugin_gsoap_2.6.a


mbranco - 10 August 2005
